{
  "stem": "4113.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was black marketeering going on, lots of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I had a heyday, because the German soldiers would come in and I could buy from them German script.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know whether you will know what scripts are that the American military had in Europe, had different dollars they could exchange in Germany.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They also had different marks for the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was a black market going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I used to buy those for Polish zlotys, and then I would sell it to another Jewish kid, you know, and I would-- for double that, you know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So people were doing all these things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, there was no shooting at that time, aside from that initial marching and killing that I just described to you.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Things were quiet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was hard, lots of hardship.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Schools were closed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Believe it or not, schooling was going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had a teacher coming and-- and teach us, my sister, me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we tried to live an ordinary life as best as we could.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There were no ghettos yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then, of course, a month or two months later, Jews were ordered to wear the Star of David armband.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we all had to wear that to be recognized.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, even so, we worked for Germans a lot, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In all honesty, I have to say, I never heard an anti-Semitic word.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "At no time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "One episode only, where a Sergeant asked me to take his-- his-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] basin that he washes, washing basin out and throw it out.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I told him that wasn't what I was here for.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I was here to work glazing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he came over and he hit me over the face.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
